FBIS4-35170 "drlat126_a_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-126 Daily Report 29 Jun 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Farm Managers Receive Performance-Based Salary Farm Managers Receive Performance-Based Salary FL2906134994 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 0900 GMT 29 Jun 94 FL2906134994 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [From the "Doing Radio" program] [Text] Farming sector managers have begun receiving a salary in accordance with the results of their performance. This experience is taking place in Urbano Noris Municipality, in Holguin Province. This experience could be extended to the rest of Cuba.
